description: The skill reads the script for The Resistance. It is configurable by adding whatever roles you might want from the Resistance Assassin module. This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by the makers of The Resistance.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask resistance reader to add role commander
Alexa, ask resistance reader to read the script
name: Resistance Reader
shortDescription: Tired of reading the script for The Resistance? Let Alexa do it for you!
